des:
You can ask Alexa to turn on or off your smart devices, bringing greater comfort to your day-to-day life, with just a voice command and you're done.

To make this possible, follow the steps below:
1. Download our "Alumbra Vivax" app from the Google Play Store or Apple Store;
2. Create your account to access the app;
3. You need to have some "Alumbra" smart devices to configure.
4. Configure that device and change the name to one that is appropriate for your use, such as "Bedroom Light";
5. Download the Amazon Alexa app and register, if you have purchased an Echo, configure it;
6. In the "Alumbra Vivax" app, click on the "me" tab and then on the "Third-Party Voice Services" options, click on "Alexa";
7. The link will be made automatically, just authorize the app and you're done.

"Alexa, turn on the bedroom light!"
"Alexa, turn on the kitchen light!"
"Alexa, turn off all the lights!"
